              </p>
              <button onclick='window.location.href="./video.html"' class="bg-green-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition duration-300">
                Join Now
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      
  
        <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
