              </p>
              <button class="bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-300">
                Register Now
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
      
     
      <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-6">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
          <p>&copy; २०८१ FitConnect. All rights reserved.</p>
          <p>
            Contact us: <a href="mailto:info@fitconnect.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">info@fitconnect.com</a>
          </p>
